Story
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a Monkey who resided on a mango tree,which wa on the banks of the river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The monkey offered him some fruits.The crocodile came backthe next day, as he loved them.The crocodile and monkey became good friends.

one day the monkey sent some fruits to crocodile's wife.she ate it and like them.But she was jealous and told the crocodile "if the druits were so delicious , monkey's heart would be so get me the heat of the monkey".the crocodile was not willing to kill his friend but he had no choice.